info.author: Daniel Schoenbohm
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: eezo
info.summary: Eezo's Dashboard streamlines the management of AI agents via its API, offering a user-friendly interface that requires minimal coding. It enables easy access for all team members, fostering agent interaction and collaboration. The platform also features real-time data sharing with interactive charts, making it an ideal solution for developers and companies looking to centralize their AI tools and processes.
